<subSubSection lastPageId="18" lastPageNumber="63" pageId="16" pageNumber="61" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="16.[189,334,1238,1264]" box="[189,334,1238,1264]" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,334,1238,1264]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="16" pageNumber="61" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,334,1238,1264]" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">Description</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="16.[189,853,1284,1311]" box="[189,853,1284,1311]" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">
MEASUREMENTS. Body length: male 7.0– 
<quantity box="[663,752,1284,1311]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.5" pageId="16" pageNumber="61" unit="mm" value="7.5">7.5 mm</quantity>
(N = 2).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="16.[188,1400,1350,1552]" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">
COLORATION. General color yellowish white (
<figureCitation box="[717,845,1350,1376]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="17.[189,232,1856,1882]" captionTargetBox="[232,1337,263,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-99@17.[232,1355,255,1827]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="Fig. 9. Andes pallidus Wang &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♂. A. Dorsal view. B. Lateral view. C. Head and thorax, dorsal view. D. Face, ventral view. E. Forewing. F. Genitalia, lateral view. G. Pygofer and gonostyli, ventral view. H. Anal segment, dorsal view. I. Gonostyli, lateral view. J. Aedeagus, right side. K. Aedeagus, left side. L. Aedeagus, dorsal view. M. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: A–D, F–M = 0.5 mm; E = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862193" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6862193/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">Fig. 9A–B</figureCitation>
). Eyes brown, ocelli light red, semi-translucent. Antenna, vertex and face yellowish white. Rostrum yellowish brown. Anterior parts of pronotum white, posterior parts yellowish brown. Mesonotum yellowish brown. Forewing semi-translucent, whitish, costal vein with 3 small, spaced dark brown spots, from centre of ScP+ RA to near claval fork with a fawn-coloured stripe; middle part of clavus and behind clavus with an irregular puce spot, respectively; apical half of wing with yellowish brown patches.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="16.[189,1399,1591,1794]" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">
HEAD AND THORAX. Vertex (
<figureCitation box="[520,647,1591,1618]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="17.[189,232,1856,1882]" captionTargetBox="[232,1337,263,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-99@17.[232,1355,255,1827]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="Fig. 9. Andes pallidus Wang &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♂. A. Dorsal view. B. Lateral view. C. Head and thorax, dorsal view. D. Face, ventral view. E. Forewing. F. Genitalia, lateral view. G. Pygofer and gonostyli, ventral view. H. Anal segment, dorsal view. I. Gonostyli, lateral view. J. Aedeagus, right side. K. Aedeagus, left side. L. Aedeagus, dorsal view. M. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: A–D, F–M = 0.5 mm; E = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862193" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6862193/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">Fig. 9A, C</figureCitation>
) 1.8× as long as wide; lateral carinae strongly elevated, median carina absent. Frons (
<figureCitation box="[449,544,1627,1653]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="17.[189,232,1856,1882]" captionTargetBox="[232,1337,263,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-99@17.[232,1355,255,1827]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="Fig. 9. Andes pallidus Wang &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♂. A. Dorsal view. B. Lateral view. C. Head and thorax, dorsal view. D. Face, ventral view. E. Forewing. F. Genitalia, lateral view. G. Pygofer and gonostyli, ventral view. H. Anal segment, dorsal view. I. Gonostyli, lateral view. J. Aedeagus, right side. K. Aedeagus, left side. L. Aedeagus, dorsal view. M. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: A–D, F–M = 0.5 mm; E = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862193" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6862193/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">Fig. 9D</figureCitation>
) 2.7× as long as wide. Pronotum (
<figureCitation box="[969,1100,1627,1653]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="17.[189,232,1856,1882]" captionTargetBox="[232,1337,263,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-99@17.[232,1355,255,1827]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="Fig. 9. Andes pallidus Wang &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♂. A. Dorsal view. B. Lateral view. C. Head and thorax, dorsal view. D. Face, ventral view. E. Forewing. F. Genitalia, lateral view. G. Pygofer and gonostyli, ventral view. H. Anal segment, dorsal view. I. Gonostyli, lateral view. J. Aedeagus, right side. K. Aedeagus, left side. L. Aedeagus, dorsal view. M. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: A–D, F–M = 0.5 mm; E = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862193" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6862193/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">Fig. 9A, C</figureCitation>
) 1.1× as long as vertex; posterior margin forming a right angle. Mesonotum 1.1× as long as pronotum and vertex combined. Forewing (
<figureCitation box="[317,439,1697,1723]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="17.[189,232,1856,1882]" captionTargetBox="[232,1337,263,1824]" captionTargetId="figure-99@17.[232,1355,255,1827]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="Fig. 9. Andes pallidus Wang &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♂. A. Dorsal view. B. Lateral view. C. Head and thorax, dorsal view. D. Face, ventral view. E. Forewing. F. Genitalia, lateral view. G. Pygofer and gonostyli, ventral view. H. Anal segment, dorsal view. I. Gonostyli, lateral view. J. Aedeagus, right side. K. Aedeagus, left side. L. Aedeagus, dorsal view. M. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: A–D, F–M = 0.5 mm; E = 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862193" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6862193/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">Fig. 9B, E</figureCitation>
) 2.3× as long as wide, with thirteen apical cells and six subapical cells; RP with 4 branches; MP with 5 branches: MP 
<subScript attach="right" box="[591,607,1751,1765]" fontSize="6" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">11</subScript>
, MP 
<subScript attach="left" box="[662,679,1751,1765]" fontSize="6" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">12</subScript>
, MP 
<subScript attach="left" box="[734,743,1751,1765]" fontSize="6" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">2</subScript>
, MP 
<subScript attach="left" box="[798,807,1751,1765]" fontSize="6" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">3</subScript>
and MP 
<subScript attach="left" box="[902,911,1751,1765]" fontSize="6" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">4</subScript>
; fork MP 
<subScript attach="left" box="[1021,1030,1751,1765]" fontSize="6" pageId="16" pageNumber="61">1</subScript>
